name: HolidayTracker
0:
”Alexa, open holiday tracker”
”Alexa, start holiday tracker”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: holiday tracker
des:
Open the skill and Alexa will automatically tell you how many days remain until all your upcoming events. Alexa can also remind you about the exact date for a specific events.
 Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
Give Alexa a holiday, and she'll countdown the days to the holiday. OR Give Alexa a date, and she'll countdown the days to your date.
